{"tid":598660,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻貓三日無痾屎，係咪有問題？","createTime":"2018-03-19T16:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T22:01:11.000Z","uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a2a01574a319dfe856f5731154cf911eaa331d9","tid":598660,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:54:19.000Z","msg":"我隻貓貓最近膀胱炎，痾唔到尿<br />\n所以轉左食全濕糧<br />\n睇左醫生， 又食緊抗生素<br />\n佢依家痾勁勁勁勁多尿<br />\n但三日幾乎無痾屎<br />\n（只有一粒，仲短過手指尾）<br />\n係食抗生素先搞到便秘？<br />\n定係有問題？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我上網搵過<br />\n有人又話食全濕糧會痾好少屎<br />\n一星期一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家嘅主子有無試過咁⋯⋯⋯ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪要帶佢去覆下診<br />\n醫生會唔會笑我on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e35ba051d1afa673b0507b50d6752703c5ce6b","tid":598660,"uid":106506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"樓主你訓醒個時有無覺得個口甘甘苦苦地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4edccf80b075980d50f2ffefbde7fcd4887e87","tid":598660,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2e35ba051d1afa673b0507b50d6752703c5ce6b","tid":598660,"uid":106506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"樓主你訓醒個時有無覺得個口甘甘苦苦地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T17:06:21.000Z","msg":"唔通夢遊食左佢啲屎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196d5dd20b395443b0ece97a76864fa4fb20d27b","tid":598660,"uid":35930,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"